text = "You look at the parking lot. There is indeed a white Opel Astra. Through the rear window you can see a leather suitcase in the back. You unlock the car and open the leather suitcase. Inside are shirts and other clothes, neatly sorted. You push a few socks to the side and find several bundles of money and a German and a Soviet passport. In the German passport a tired-looking Boris Amburger looks at you. Born in Mulda, Saxony. In the old Soviet passport a young man in uniform, born in Moscow.

You take the passports, close the suitcase and lock the Opel. You get into your car and send a radio message. It might be a while before your colleagues arrive. On the way there you saw a bakery. You now feel like having something warm to drink and maybe a roll for 35 cents."
